data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with two living areas, an open floor plan, a separate laundry room, and a nice large backyard! As soon as you step inside, you'll find yourself in a big living area connected to a formal dining room. The kitchen boasts some stainless steel appliances and an open floor plan that leads to the second living space. The downstairs spaces are adorned with beautiful tiles, and the bedrooms upstairs come with carpet and tiles, each fitted with a ceiling fan. The home also features a large two-car garage and refrigerated air, rounding out the great amenities it has to offer.
